reviewText: Fantastic movies. They arrived within the estimated time, and they are both in one CD box, that is convenient.
Love these movies and now I have them at a great price, on DVD

I'm converting my VHS collection to DVD & was glad to find these 2 Trek favorites on one DVD. I really liked ALL the Trek movies, but the TNG movies were a breath of fresh air for the series. Recommended for ALL Trek fans!

Great science fiction. As a fan of both the original and new Star Trek, the movies are great. The old series Star Trek became very trite after the Gene Roddenberry, the creator of the series, left the show; but it was really innovative for its time. The new Star Trek series was an instant hit because it went back to the original premise of science instead of formula tv.
We wanted the First Contact which this had it. The added bonus was the New Generation. Which was great too.
It's a combination of the star trek next generation cast  & the original star trek cast of capt. Kirk, McCoy & Spock. A pretty unique story with all of them. I really liked it.
Got to complete all 10 Star Trek movies.
Great movies. My hubby is a trekkie, and I am so not into it. But I liked these. Great deal.

I am a Star Trek fan and as much as I love the original cast and crew on the Star Ship Enterprise, I love the Next Generations series as well, action packed great characters.  Patrick Stewart makes a great Captain!
I got the first 6 movies and had to get 7 and 8.  Glad to add them to my collection.

Love, love, love. <3 <3 <3

1st Contact is so well done, it is timeless.
The sound on star trek 2 is not synced up, looks like I'm watching a Japanese movie
These are  two  very  dramatic  movies. Glad  to  be  able  to  get  them  together  like  this .  Love  this kind  of  Sci Fi. Great  caricatures .
Watched this movie several times and enjoy it every time, now I have it in my collection

Great movie's, I am not a fan of the newer releases of the Star Trek movies, I like the Utopian theme of the TNG, the Idea that the future will be better and all the old crappy ideals and Biases of the past are finally gotten rid of. So I like these movies and the actors and actresses who play in them. In the best traditions of Star Trek, these are great.
